    <h1>Average Revenue Per User (ARPU)</h1>
    <p class="description">Total revenue divided by the number of active users in a period. ARPU tells you how much each customer is worth on average and is the north-star metric for pricing, expansion, and forecasting in subscription businesses.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
