          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">How do I increase ARPU without raising prices?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Focus on expansion revenue: package usage-based add-ons, upsell to higher tiers when usage crosses a threshold, and cross-sell adjacent products. Improving the mix of paid seats vs free seats often moves ARPU faster than a price hike.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Should I optimize for more users or higher ARPU?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Early-stage teams should chase user growth to validate demand. Once retention is proven, shift toward ARPU expansion because it compounds without the acquisition cost of new logos.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">What is the difference between ARPU and ARPPU?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>ARPU divides revenue by all users, including free ones. ARPPU divides revenue by paying users only. ARPPU is more useful when a freemium or trial funnel dilutes the ARPU number.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">How often should I track ARPU?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Monthly for subscription products, quarterly for enterprise. Weekly ARPU is noisy for most businesses because it does not reflect the billing cycle.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

